revision.text: Time Flute increases the player's Gym and Dungeon Timers by a base 2%. The Base effect is multiplied by the players Achievement Bonus, to a current maximum of 22%, with an achievement bonus of 1000%. Costs a variable amount of Ground, Poison, and Steel Gems when active, cost based on how many total Flutes are active.
